        "description": [
            "<u>The cottontail</u> puzzles over the receding landscape, the foliage growing ever more curled and brown, sun-facing limbs sacrificed in the outstretched heat to bestow the slightest noon-day respite to those underneath... though little relief when the fires come.",
            "<u>The hare</u> can still remember what a fresh rainy spring felt like, the sudden pours of invigoration, huddling underground and waiting to smell the sun and water, summer, fall, and winter",
            "<u>The volcanoo rabbit</u> samples the breeze, the air tasting hostile, saping the eyes, piercing the throat, withering lungs, and desiccating leaves",
            "<u>The swamp rabbit</u> hears the ocean, lap higher and further inland, waters uncomfortably warm, acidic and destitute"
        ],
